title: Motor.Rock+Update.1.to.5-SKIDROW
description:
Motor.Rock and Update.1.to.5-SKIDROW



Changelog Update:


Motor Rock Update 5 info:

- fixed: continuous graphics lags in windowed mode and on some mobile cards and weak discrete cards, removed option fixed framerate


Motor Rock Update 4 info:

- fixed minor bugs in the models
- fixed problems of the run of the game on some mobile graphics cards 
- performance optimization


Motor Rock Update 3 info:

- removed the need to install physx drivers
- fixed start problems on some video from the initialization of textures
- fixed problems with drm (start problems), likely
- minor fixes


Motor Rock Update 2 info:

- added high quality monstertruck and new models of destroyed cars. And of course there are bug fixes and improvements on the game balance (4 - 5 planets)


Motor Rock Update 1 info:

- reducing Difficulty all the planets and bug fixes Steam Lobby

By the way. Soon to be added to the game a new Monstertruck!
